==In media==

A fictional Duke of Edinburgh appears in the 1983 sitcom &quot;The Black Adder&quot;. Rowan Atkinson plays the title character, Prince Edmund, who is granted the title Duke of Edinburgh by his father, a fictitious King Richard IV.

